ization problem (SOP) whose objective is to\nmaximize scalability by managing the spectrum sharing across the SNOWs. By\nproving the NP-hardness of SOP, we then propose two polynomial-time methods to\nsolve it: a greedy heuristic algorithm and a 1/2-approximation algorithm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Aug 2020 21:12:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-01"}
